name: Tenants (Inquilinos)
description:
You are a mite that has to protect its home crossing the stage to reach the plug of a vacuum cleaner which is destroying your home and is menacing to take your family. Through the way you will find some obstacles, as holes through which you can be aspirated.

Eres un ácaro que tiene que proteger su hogar cruzando la fase para llegar al enchufe y desconectar la aspiradora que está destruyendo tu hogar y amenaza con llevarse a tu familia. Por el camino encontrarás una serie de obstáculos, como agujeros por donde la aspiradora puede succionarte.
